Demmette Guidry bụ onye isi ụlọ ọrụ egwu America, ónyé njikwa talent na ónyé nwe akara, ónyé nyèrè aka ịmalite ọrụ nke ọtụtụ ndị na-edekọ egwu a ma ama gụnyere Beyoncé, Lauryn Hill, Maxwell, Cypress Hill, Mary Mary, Alicia Keys na ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ.
Entertainment, LLC nke dị na Atlanta na D-Media, LLC, nke na-agụnye ahịa, mmepụta, nkwalite na nkesa nke ngwaahịa ntụrụndụ égwu.

Guidry jere ozi n'ọtụtụ ọrụ ndị isi dị ka ónyé ọchụnta ego na ọkachasị dị ka onye isi ụlọ ọrụ na ikike nke osote ónyé isi oche nke Marketing na mgbe e mesịrị onye isi oche màkà Columbia Records, ónyé isi oche oche nke Urban Music maka Warner Bros. Ihe ndekọ na osote onye isi oche, General Manager for Music World Entertainment / Sanctuary Urban.

Guidry bi na Atlanta, GA, ma bụrụkwa ónyé guzobere Black American Music Association, otu 501(c)(6) ụlọ ọrụ azụmahịa nkè e guzobere iji chekwaa, chebe, ma kwalite ihe nketa na ọdịnihu nké Authentic Black American Music
